snippet.title: Moonshell Island Mini Teaser
snippet.description:
Achieve dreams, build a community & save Moonshell Island from Nomsters in this magical action-RPG combining Zelda-like gameplay and story-driven simulation elements.

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1629660

Release Date: TBD
Platforms: PC

Teaser Demo available now to our Patreon supporters!
https://www.patreon.com/cheekynauts

Developed by Cheekynauts Entertainment Ltd.
http://www.cheekynauts.com
https://twitter.com/Cheekynauts

Music by Anna E. (https://annaeichenauermusic.com) aka @queergermangirl (https://twitter.com/QueerGermanGirl)
